      511          0.0.0.0:8080       0.0.0.0:*    users:((\"node\",pid=225,fd=22))                       \ntcp   LISTEN 0      100        127.0.0.1:25         0.0.0.0:*    users:((\"master\",pid=281,fd=13))                     \ntcp   LISTEN 0      511        127.0.0.1:18792      0.0.0.0:*    users:((\"openclaw-gatewa\",pid=474897,fd=29))         \ntcp   LISTEN 0      511        127.0.0.1:18791      0.0.0.0:*    users:((\"openclaw-gatewa\",pid=474897,fd=27))         \ntcp   LISTEN 0      4096               *:22               *:*    users:((\"sshd\",pid=116,fd=3),(\"systemd\",pid=1,fd=45))\ntcp   LISTEN 0      100            [::1]:25            [::]:*    users:((\"master\",pid=281,fd=14))","cwd":"/home/zbb/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773795120486}}
{"type":"message","id":"73e32dee","parentId":"ec51c282","timestamp":"2026-03-18T00:52:09.325Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 有。\n\n我这边看到监听在 `127.0.0.1` 的有这几个：\n\n- `127.0.0.1:25` → `master`（Postfix）\n- `127.0.0.1:18791` → `openclaw-gatewa`\n- `127.0.0.1:18792` → `openclaw-gatewa`\n\n另外，**不只监听本地回环**，还有这些对外监听：\n\n- `0.0.0.0:18789` → `openclaw-gatewa`\n- `0.0.0.0:8080` → `node`\n- `*:22` → `sshd`\n\n如果你要查的是“某个服务是不是只绑在 127.0.0.1，而不是对外网开放”，那答案是：**有些是只绑本地，有些不是。**\n\n如果你愿意，我可以继续帮你：\n1. 查 `18789/18791/18792` 分别是什么用途  \n2. 查 `8080` 是哪个 Node 服务  \n3. 判断哪些端口有暴露风险"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":956,"output":257,"cacheRead":37376,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":38589,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773795120491}}
