to restrict senders.                 │\n│  - Run: openclaw security audit --deep                                   │\n│                                                                          │\n├──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────╯\n│\n◇  Skills status ────────────╮\n│                            │\n│  Eligible: 31              │\n│  Missing requirements: 46  │\n│  Blocked by allowlist: 0   │\n│                            │\n├────────────────────────────╯\n│\n◇  Plugins ──────╮\n│                │\n│  Loaded: 3     │\n│  Disabled: 39  │\n│  Errors: 0     │\n│                │\n├────────────────╯\n│\n◇  Plugin diagnostics ─────────────────────────────────────────────────╮\n│                                                                      │\n│  - ERROR openclaw-lark: channel already registered: feishu (feishu)  │\n│    (/home/zbb/.openclaw/extensions/openclaw-lark/index.js)               │\n│                                                                      │\n├──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────╯\nFeishu: ok\nAgents: main (default)\nHeartbeat interval: 30m (main)\nSession store (main): /home/zbb/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions/sessions.json (5 entries)\n- agent:main:feishu:direct:ou_664eb5978d7a2e16127187d1c18827d3 (1m ago)\n- agent:main:cron:fe4e985f-3f32-4015-89d7-3114e3b3a6bb (356m ago)\n- agent:main:cron:fe4e985f-3f32-4015-89d7-3114e3b3a6bb:run:dd957211-0f63-42a6-bb32-f033c1cb0e28 (356m ago)\n- agent:main:feishu:group:oc_3f35394f236997ca78b509c9fb71a383 (576m ago)\n- agent:main:main (1977m ago)\n│\n◇  Memory search ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────╮\n│                                                                          │\n│  Memory search is enabled but no embedding provider is configured.       │\n│  Semantic recall will not work without an embedding provider.            │\n│  Gateway memory probe for default agent is not ready: No API key found   │\n│