{"type":"message","id":"a81a755d","parentId":"6b0960f2","timestamp":"2026-03-18T00:56:47.469Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Diagnosing gateway issues**\n\nI need to figure out if the device or cron failures are related to the gateway closing on ws://127.0.0.1:18789. The logs show a failure with the gateway connection on command, which might mean the commands are failing due to this instability. It seems we might want to suggest restarting the gateway or using the gateway tool. I’ll confirm that these failures align with the connection issue, but it's not about 127.0.0.1 itself.\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]]对，这次基本能对上了——**不是“监听了 127.0.0.1”本身有问题，而是 CLI 连到网关后，网关把连接关掉了。**\n\n我这边刚查到的关键信息是：\n\n- `openclaw logs --limit 120 --plain` 返回：\n  - `gateway connect failed: Error: gateway closed (1000)`\n  - `Gateway target: ws://127.0.0.1:18789`\n- `openclaw doctor` 里也提示了网关相关异常迹象\n\n所以更准确的判断是：\n\n### 结论\n`openclaw cron list` 和 `openclaw devices list` 失败，**更像是网关 RPC 通道有问题**，不是因为“CLI 不能访问 127.0.0.1”。\n\n因为：\n\n- 这台机器本机访问 `127.0.0.1` 本来就应该是通的\n- `18789` 也确实在监听\n- 但实际连上后，**gateway 直接 closed (1000)**\n\n也就是说问题更像是：\n\n1. **网关进程状态异常 / 半活着**\n   - 端口在监听\n   - 但某些 RPC 请求进来就断开\n\n2. **CLI 和 gateway 状态不一致**\n   - 比如网关升级后卡住、旧进程残留、内部服务没准备好\n\n3. **插件/通道初始化有冲突**\n   - doctor 里有一条：\n     - `ERROR openclaw-lark: channel already registered: feishu (feishu)`\n   - 这未必就是根因，但说明启动过程里**有插件注册冲突**\n\n---\n\n### 你前面那个猜测，修正成一句话就是：\n- **不是因为它绑在 127.0.0.1**\n- **而是因为 CLI 目标是 `ws://127.0.0.1:18789`，但这个网关连接被异常关闭了**\n\n---\n\n### 现在最像的处理办法\n先做这个：\n\n```bash\nopenclaw gateway restart\n```\n\n然后再试：\n\n```bash\nopenclaw cron list\nopenclaw devices list\n```\n\n---\n\n### 如果重启后还不行，再查这几个方向\n1. **网关日志**\n   - 看重启后有没有新的报错\n2. **Feishu / 插件重复注册**\n   - `channel already registered: feishu`\n3. **版本/运行时问题**\n   - doctor 里提到 gateway 现在是从：\n     - `/home/zbb/.nvm/versions/node/v24.14.0/bin/node`\n   - 说明它依赖 nvm 环境，不是最稳的 system node\n4. **网关配置**\n   - 尤其是 bind / remote / token / plugin entries\n\n---\n\n### 我给你的判断优先级\n- **高概率**：gateway RPC 本身异常\n- **低概率**：单纯因为 127.0.0.1 绑定导致本机 CLI 失败\n- **中概率伴随因素**：feishu 插件重复注册 / gateway 启动不完整\n\n如果你要，我下一步可以直接继续帮你：\n1. 检查当前 gateway 进程和端口对应关系  \n2. 看重启后日志  \n3. 顺手把 `cron list` / `devices list` 复测一遍\n\n你回我一句“继续查”就行。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":38494,"output":1241,"cacheRead":2560,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":42295,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773795382605}}
{"type":"message","id":"33728538","parentId":"a81a755d","timestamp":"2026-03-18T00:56:50.561Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54abccbed8acb379a2a8bec8f0c\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_664eb5978d7a2e16127187d1c18827d3\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_664eb5978d7a2e16127187d1c18827d3\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Wed 2026-03-18 08:56 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_664eb5978d7a2e16127187d1c18827d3\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_664eb5978d7a2e16127187d1c18827d3\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_664eb5978d7a2e16127187d1c18827d3\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b54abccbed8acb379a2a8bec8f0c]\nou_664eb5978d7a2e16127187d1c18827d3: 如果网关卡死 你为啥还活着"}],"timestamp":1773795410558}}
{"type":"message","id":"95e8b93e","parentId":"33728538","timestamp":"2026-03-18T00:57:08.703Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Exploring agent runtimes**\n\nI think I need to address the conceptual differences between a gateway and the current agent runtime. It’s interesting to consider how one operates independently while the other functions within a direct session, not going through the CLI. I should clarify these distinctions in the answer while being careful to obey any reply tags that may apply. Keeping it clear and informative is essential!\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 因为我现在这条会话，**不等于你本机 `openclaw` CLI 到网关的那条链路**。\n\n更直白点：\n\n- **你现在在飞书里跟我说话**\n- 这条消息是 **OpenClaw 已经跑起来的主会话** 在处理\n- 而 `openclaw cron list` / `openclaw devices list` 是 **新启动一个 CLI 进程，再去连 gateway websocket**\n- 现在坏掉的，像是 **CLI → gateway 这段**\n- 不代表 **已经在跑的 agent/session** 立刻一起死掉\n\n所以会出现这种状态：\n\n1. **老连接/已有进程还活着**  \n   我这边还能继续回你。\n\n2. **新 CLI 连接建不起来**  \n   `openclaw cron list`、`openclaw devices list` 这种就报错。\n\n3. **网关可能是“半死不活”**  \n   端口还在监听，但对新 websocket 连接不正常，或者接了马上关。\n\n这其实挺像：\n\n- 店门还开着\n- 里面老顾客还坐着\n- 但新顾客一进门就被店员推出去\n\n所以“我还活着”**恰恰说明不是整个进程树全灭**，而更像是：\n\n- gateway 的 websocket 接入层异常\n- gateway 某个内部状态卡死\n- 或 session/插件冲突把新连接搞崩了\n\n另外 `doctor` 里有个可疑点：\n\n- `ERROR openclaw-lark: channel already registered: feishu (feishu)`\n\n这不一定是元凶，但说明**插件装载状态不太干净**，确实有“半异常运行”的味道。\n\n我目前判断优先级大概是：\n\n- **最高概率**：gateway 半卡死 / 新连接处理异常\n- **次高**：插件注册冲突引发 CLI 初始化或握手异常\n- **较低**：单纯监听地址问题\n\n如果你要，我下一步建议直接做两件事里的一件：\n\n- **稳妥**：先 `openclaw gateway restart`\n- **更细查**：我继续帮你查配置和进程关系，看看是不是 Feishu 插件重复注册把 gateway 弄脏了\n\n我个人偏向先重启网关，成本最低，最像能直接恢复 CLI 的解法。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":7221,"output":625,"cacheRead":36352,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":44198,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773795410560}}
